<%- include('header'); -%>
<main>
  <div class="home">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h1>Home</h1>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="section-content">
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque non
        diam justo. Quisque suscipit egestas porttitor. In dapibus, purus nec
        vestibulum dignissim, tortor velit fringilla velit, at imperdiet est
        elit ut felis. Ut vitae justo facilisis magna sollicitudin iaculis
        sodales lobortis tellus. Nullam dui ipsum, congue vitae ullamcorper
        eget, fermentum eu massa. Integer in euismod augue. Pellentesque eget
        laoreet sapien.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-title">
    <h1>Recent Posts</h1>
  </div>
  <hr />
  <% blogPosts.forEach(post => { %>
  <div class="blog-post__items">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="blog-post-title">
        <h2><%=post.title%></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-post-date">
        <h3><%=post.date%></h3>
      </div>
      <div id="post-content"><%=post.content%></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%});%>
</main>

<%- include('footer'); -%>
